1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:10,000
[English subtitles are available]

2
00:01:36,350 --> 00:01:42,270
[I Don't Want To Be Friends With You]

3
00:01:42,820 --> 00:01:44,020
Senior year?

4
00:01:46,270 --> 00:01:48,280
Senior year means we
finally become adults.

5
00:01:48,280 --> 00:01:49,770
We can do what we want to do.

6
00:01:50,280 --> 00:01:52,280
We can express love to the girls we like.

7
00:01:57,170 --> 00:01:58,420
I can't say this?

8
00:02:01,810 --> 00:02:03,490
Although I did not have a good grade,

9
00:02:03,490 --> 00:02:05,130
I value the college entrance examination.

10
00:02:05,130 --> 00:02:05,780
Think about it.

11
00:02:05,780 --> 00:02:07,420
If everyone is admitted to university,

12
00:02:07,420 --> 00:02:08,370
only I am not...

13
00:02:08,370 --> 00:02:09,330
How terrible that is!

14
00:02:09,330 --> 00:02:11,500
I don't want to work at my family
snack bar after graduation.

15
00:02:11,810 --> 00:02:12,930
I just want to know

16
00:02:13,330 --> 00:02:15,710
if all the minor subjects will be
cancelled in senior year.

17
00:02:16,170 --> 00:02:17,410
No more Physical Education Class?

18
00:02:20,650 --> 00:02:21,250
I understand.

19
00:02:22,090 --> 00:02:22,810
I will obey the arrangement.

20
00:02:23,170 --> 00:02:24,650
We should study hard in our senior year.

21
00:02:24,850 --> 00:02:25,850
We should try our best.

22
00:02:26,290 --> 00:02:28,290
I want to learn acting after graduation.

23
00:02:28,290 --> 00:02:30,610
Because acting has always been my dream.

24
00:02:30,610 --> 00:02:32,490
Unfortunately, it has never been realized.

25
00:02:32,490 --> 00:02:34,610
I never care what Li Qing Tong says.

26
00:02:34,610 --> 00:02:35,170
Really.

27
00:02:37,090 --> 00:02:38,490
Because I think she has a problem

28
00:02:38,780 --> 00:02:39,490
right here.

29
00:02:39,850 --> 00:02:41,930
I think I can do well in
the college entrance examination.

30
00:02:42,210 --> 00:02:44,090
I have a great leap
in my exam results now.

31
00:02:44,490 --> 00:02:46,710
I would like to thank
Wu Zhi Xun in particular.

32
00:02:48,579 --> 00:02:49,329
And

33
00:02:49,329 --> 00:02:49,970
Mr. Wu,

34
00:02:50,570 --> 00:02:51,270
the head of department,

35
00:02:51,290 --> 00:02:51,810
and,

36
00:02:52,250 --> 00:02:52,980
our teachers.

37
00:02:54,530 --> 00:02:55,430
My goal?

38
00:02:56,290 --> 00:02:59,490
My goal is to help Li Qing Tong
enter a good university.

39
00:03:01,690 --> 00:03:02,170
Wait,

40
00:03:02,440 --> 00:03:03,890
why are you laughing?

41
00:03:03,890 --> 00:03:04,490
I mean it.

42
00:03:05,210 --> 00:03:07,720
What's different in senior year?

43
00:03:08,210 --> 00:03:09,010
Nothing.

44
00:03:09,410 --> 00:03:10,970
It's all the same to me.

45
00:03:11,490 --> 00:03:13,340
This is my second time in senior year.

46
00:03:13,340 --> 00:03:14,690
I had said what I wanted to say last year.

47
00:03:17,970 --> 00:03:18,620
Well,

48
00:03:18,620 --> 00:03:19,329
senior year...

49
00:03:19,850 --> 00:03:20,610
Mr. Wu, Mr. Wu!

50
00:03:20,820 --> 00:03:21,700
We're sorry but

51
00:03:21,700 --> 00:03:23,970
this part is for students to talk
about their feelings on senior year.

52
00:03:23,970 --> 00:03:25,220
The teachers are excluded.

53
00:03:31,400 --> 00:03:35,930
[Episode 12: Senior Year Is Finally Here]

54
00:03:49,010 --> 00:03:49,890
What's the smell?

55
00:03:53,240 --> 00:03:54,240
What are you doing?

56
00:03:55,050 --> 00:03:55,880
Eating instant noodles.

57
00:03:57,370 --> 00:03:59,250
We are having a self-study class now.

58
00:04:00,370 --> 00:04:01,840
Can't I be hungry in the self-study class?

59
00:04:02,600 --> 00:04:03,690
You disturbed other students.

60
00:04:05,610 --> 00:04:07,440
How did I disturb you two
with just some instant noodle?

61
00:04:07,440 --> 00:04:08,490
Why are you so impressionable?

62
00:04:09,170 --> 00:04:10,330
If you don't want to sit here,
just go to the front.

63
00:04:10,330 --> 00:04:11,690
No one's forcing you to sit here.

64
00:04:15,480 --> 00:04:16,050
Come here.

65
00:04:24,050 --> 00:04:24,970
Chen Jun He,

66
00:04:25,150 --> 00:04:26,250
what do you want to do?

67
00:04:27,140 --> 00:04:28,360
Why are you angry?

68
00:04:28,710 --> 00:04:29,440
You can have some.

69
00:04:29,440 --> 00:04:29,810
Here.

70
00:04:29,810 --> 00:04:30,250
Calm down.

71
00:04:31,640 --> 00:04:32,960
If you want to eat,
go out and eat by yourself.

72
00:04:34,490 --> 00:04:35,210
What are you three doing?

73
00:04:36,409 --> 00:04:37,090
Eating?

74
00:04:38,480 --> 00:04:39,850
Go out!

75
00:04:55,740 --> 00:04:57,040
You three are now having

76
00:04:58,420 --> 00:04:59,580
a bowl of noodles together.

77
00:05:00,240 --> 00:05:01,450
Friendship is brewing?

78
00:05:02,380 --> 00:05:03,330
Sir, we were not...

79
00:05:03,330 --> 00:05:04,580
Shut up, please.

80
00:05:05,330 --> 00:05:06,510
What did you promise me back then?

81
00:05:07,130 --> 00:05:08,130
Study hard,

82
00:05:08,130 --> 00:05:08,770
and obey the rules.

83
00:05:08,770 --> 00:05:09,610
What did you just do?

84
00:05:10,050 --> 00:05:10,450
But we did not...

85
00:05:10,450 --> 00:05:10,940
You shut up!

86
00:05:11,770 --> 00:05:13,210
I just want to tell you three.

87
00:05:13,210 --> 00:05:14,570
From today on

88
00:05:14,570 --> 00:05:15,950
I don't care about you.

89
00:05:15,950 --> 00:05:17,210
You can be yourselves.

90
00:05:17,210 --> 00:05:18,170
Including you,

91
00:05:19,010 --> 00:05:19,770
understand?

92
00:05:19,770 --> 00:05:20,810
You can do whatever you want.

93
00:05:20,810 --> 00:05:21,810
You want to eat noodles?

94
00:05:21,810 --> 00:05:22,500
Go to the canteen

95
00:05:22,500 --> 00:05:23,090
whenever you want.

96
00:05:23,450 --> 00:05:24,480
Don't disturb the other students.

97
00:05:25,050 --> 00:05:25,930
I don't care about you any more.

98
00:05:40,250 --> 00:05:43,050
Am I troubling you?

99
00:05:45,159 --> 00:05:46,250
I don't want to scold you any more.

100
00:05:49,090 --> 00:05:50,050
I'm begging you now.

101
00:05:50,810 --> 00:05:52,050
Please don't bother me any more.

102
00:05:53,090 --> 00:05:54,730
This school is running out of room for me.

103
00:05:54,730 --> 00:05:56,720
You are happy if I can't
go to college, aren't you?

104
00:06:27,170 --> 00:06:28,650
Do you really have a fever?

105
00:06:28,930 --> 00:06:30,570
I am so angry.

106
00:06:30,570 --> 00:06:32,210
I am going to die from anger.

107
00:06:32,810 --> 00:06:33,850
I will talk to him tomorrow.

108
00:06:34,370 --> 00:06:36,290
Please don't.

109
00:06:36,650 --> 00:06:38,810
He's really out of his mind.

110
00:06:40,250 --> 00:06:42,930
What bad luck on earth
did I have in my last life?

111
00:06:43,370 --> 00:06:46,890
How could I provoke such a rascal?

112
00:06:55,890 --> 00:07:00,250
[Tieyuan No. 3 Middle School]

113
00:07:10,530 --> 00:07:11,290
Where's Li Qing Tong?

114
00:07:13,170 --> 00:07:13,890
She had a fever and asked for leave.

115
00:07:25,570 --> 00:07:26,770
Let's discuss something.

116
00:07:27,970 --> 00:07:29,170
You

117
00:07:29,170 --> 00:07:30,450
go back to the front.

118
00:07:31,170 --> 00:07:33,370
I promise to study hard

119
00:07:33,370 --> 00:07:34,290
and won't bother anyone.

120
00:07:34,850 --> 00:07:35,570
Never.

121
00:07:38,770 --> 00:07:39,570
Or I'll just sit here,

122
00:07:39,570 --> 00:07:40,409
and try my best to annoy you.

123
00:07:41,800 --> 00:07:42,650
Help yourself.

124
00:07:53,330 --> 00:07:53,890
Wu Zhi Xun.

125
00:07:54,250 --> 00:07:55,210
Let's start to learn!

126
00:07:58,010 --> 00:07:58,890
What are you guys looking at?

127
00:07:59,770 --> 00:08:00,650
Can't we study?

128
00:08:15,050 --> 00:08:16,530
I can't work out this question.
Can you teach me?

129
00:08:17,450 --> 00:08:18,170
I can't, too.

130
00:08:20,010 --> 00:08:21,170
Are you kidding me?

131
00:08:21,170 --> 00:08:22,570
Don't you want to help your classmate?

132
00:08:25,570 --> 00:08:26,650
What are you doing?

133
00:08:26,650 --> 00:08:27,490
You come out with me.

134
00:08:28,810 --> 00:08:30,210
Not polite at all.

135
00:08:38,350 --> 00:08:39,970
Can you stop pestering Li Qing Tong?

136
00:08:40,289 --> 00:08:41,880
It's none of your business.

137
00:08:43,130 --> 00:08:43,929
None of my business?

138
00:08:43,929 --> 00:08:45,530
Things between you two are my business.

139
00:08:46,450 --> 00:08:48,040
Don't talk about nonsense.

140
00:08:48,040 --> 00:08:49,170
What happened to Li Qing Tong?

141
00:08:49,170 --> 00:08:50,090
Why does she have a fever?

142
00:08:50,090 --> 00:08:51,770
Now you care about her?

143
00:08:51,770 --> 00:08:52,570
Continue making fun of her,

144
00:08:52,570 --> 00:08:54,130
and you will drive her crazy.

145
00:08:54,130 --> 00:08:55,410
When did I make fun of her?

146
00:08:55,410 --> 00:08:55,770
I...

147
00:08:56,290 --> 00:08:58,090
I just want to study with her, can't I?

148
00:08:58,090 --> 00:08:59,170
Study?

149
00:08:59,690 --> 00:09:01,130
Do you really study with her?

150
00:09:02,530 --> 00:09:03,460
You nasty Swift Leg!

151
00:09:03,460 --> 00:09:04,570
It's none of your business!

152
00:09:05,760 --> 00:09:06,570
What did you call me?

153
00:09:06,570 --> 00:09:07,610
Swift Leg!

154
00:09:08,050 --> 00:09:09,770
Don't you like kicking so much?

155
00:09:09,770 --> 00:09:10,770
The name suits you!

156
00:09:25,290 --> 00:09:27,010
Please give me some soup.

157
00:09:27,010 --> 00:09:28,810
I am going to die from anger.

158
00:09:29,230 --> 00:09:31,530
You are still a child.
What are you angry with?

159
00:09:32,810 --> 00:09:34,290
Can't I be angry with my poor performance?

160
00:09:35,130 --> 00:09:35,970
Well, you really should be angry then.

161
00:09:37,120 --> 00:09:37,770
Here you are, Hua.

162
00:09:41,080 --> 00:09:44,050
Why isn't dad at home at this hour?

163
00:09:44,330 --> 00:09:45,570
He didn't come back all night.

164
00:09:46,050 --> 00:09:46,970
He is busy.

165
00:09:46,970 --> 00:09:47,810
Leave him alone.

166
00:09:47,810 --> 00:09:49,610
What is he busy with every day?

167
00:09:49,610 --> 00:09:51,570
It's hard to see him now.

168
00:09:52,610 --> 00:09:54,930
Children don't need to worry about adults.

169
00:09:55,230 --> 00:09:55,930
Adults?

170
00:09:55,930 --> 00:09:56,850
I'm grown up, too.

171
00:09:56,850 --> 00:09:58,010
Can't I ask?

172
00:09:58,410 --> 00:09:59,290
How dare you talk back!

173
00:09:59,930 --> 00:10:01,010
Just eat now.

174
00:10:01,450 --> 00:10:02,490
You didn't go to school yesterday,

175
00:10:02,490 --> 00:10:03,930
so Wu Zhi Xun took notes for you.

176
00:10:03,930 --> 00:10:04,690
You should do your revision later.

177
00:10:05,570 --> 00:10:06,770
Who is Wu Zhi Xun?

178
00:10:07,810 --> 00:10:09,090
One of our classmates.

179
00:10:09,410 --> 00:10:10,050
The one...

180
00:10:10,050 --> 00:10:10,970
the one who make up lessons for us.

181
00:10:11,330 --> 00:10:12,770
Make up lessons for you?

182
00:10:13,530 --> 00:10:15,330
You can invite him here someday.

183
00:10:15,330 --> 00:10:16,650
I will make some fine dishes

184
00:10:16,650 --> 00:10:17,650
to thank him.

185
00:10:17,650 --> 00:10:18,330
Okay.

186
00:10:18,330 --> 00:10:19,210
We will invite him when possible.

187
00:10:19,690 --> 00:10:20,050
Good.

188
00:10:23,170 --> 00:10:24,530
Dad, you're back!

189
00:10:24,970 --> 00:10:25,610
I'm back.

190
00:10:26,520 --> 00:10:27,840
Why are you coughing?

191
00:10:27,840 --> 00:10:28,210
Don't worry.

192
00:10:28,210 --> 00:10:29,970
I had a bit of a cold the other day.

193
00:10:30,330 --> 00:10:31,530
I just bought medicine for Tong Tong.

194
00:10:31,530 --> 00:10:32,490
I'll give you one.

195
00:10:33,890 --> 00:10:34,290
You,

196
00:10:34,290 --> 00:10:35,050
what happened to you?

197
00:10:35,230 --> 00:10:36,090
You have a cold?

198
00:10:38,210 --> 00:10:39,610
She is in senior year,

199
00:10:39,610 --> 00:10:40,650
so she feels stressed.

200
00:10:41,010 --> 00:10:41,930
But I must tell you that

201
00:10:42,290 --> 00:10:43,800
I'm fully motivated to study now.

202
00:10:43,800 --> 00:10:45,290
I have a lot of energy when I study.

203
00:10:46,220 --> 00:10:48,450
You fail in the exam all the time.

204
00:10:48,450 --> 00:10:49,730
How come you have energy to study?

205
00:10:50,400 --> 00:10:52,490
Mom! Look at my dad.

206
00:10:52,490 --> 00:10:54,410
He doesn't know
how to encourage me at all.

207
00:10:55,050 --> 00:10:55,930
Your dad is just inconsiderate.

208
00:10:55,930 --> 00:10:56,970
Why did you say that to her?

209
00:10:57,490 --> 00:10:59,410
She's finally shown some determination.

210
00:10:59,610 --> 00:11:00,770
Why would you hurt her confidence?

211
00:11:01,010 --> 00:11:02,450
I'm just kidding.

212
00:11:02,850 --> 00:11:03,970
I'll get you a bowl.

213
00:11:03,970 --> 00:11:04,450
No, no.

214
00:11:04,450 --> 00:11:05,890
I have eaten outside.

215
00:11:08,220 --> 00:11:11,650
Dad must hope you go to university,

216
00:11:11,650 --> 00:11:12,230
don't I?

217
00:11:12,530 --> 00:11:13,690
In our Li family,

218
00:11:13,690 --> 00:11:16,230
there is no serious scholar
in the past three generations.

219
00:11:17,170 --> 00:11:19,230
At present, I have the highest education,

220
00:11:19,650 --> 00:11:20,490
the key senior high school.

221
00:11:21,130 --> 00:11:22,170
Oh, my goodness.

222
00:11:22,170 --> 00:11:23,410
Key senior high school.

223
00:11:23,410 --> 00:11:24,970
You dropped out in your freshman year.

224
00:11:24,970 --> 00:11:26,290
Key senior high school?

225
00:11:26,290 --> 00:11:27,610
How dare you say that?

226
00:11:27,610 --> 00:11:29,680
I did attend for several days.

227
00:11:29,680 --> 00:11:31,170
I didn't say I had finished
all three years.

228
00:11:31,730 --> 00:11:33,610
The three of us who studied in high school

229
00:11:33,610 --> 00:11:35,170
are discussing academic issues.

230
00:11:35,210 --> 00:11:36,350
You are just a junior high school student.

231
00:11:36,350 --> 00:11:37,930
Why are you interfering?

232
00:11:37,930 --> 00:11:38,450
I...

233
00:11:38,450 --> 00:11:39,800
Why did you say that?

234
00:11:39,800 --> 00:11:41,340
I studied in normal school.

235
00:11:41,340 --> 00:11:43,090
Don't talk about that normal school.

236
00:11:43,090 --> 00:11:45,170
Anyone who reads can be
admitted to that school.

237
00:11:45,170 --> 00:11:46,850
It is not a proper school.

238
00:11:46,850 --> 00:11:48,090
How dare you say that!

239
00:11:48,090 --> 00:11:48,690
Well,

240
00:11:48,690 --> 00:11:49,450
no more talking.

241
00:11:49,450 --> 00:11:50,230
You go on eating.

242
00:11:50,230 --> 00:11:51,450
I'll go get some sleep.

243
00:11:52,810 --> 00:11:53,770
I'll wake you up later.

244
00:11:54,170 --> 00:11:54,690
Okay.

245
00:11:58,450 --> 00:11:59,720
You two keep eating.

246
00:12:02,570 --> 00:12:03,730
Hua, have some meat.

247
00:12:18,070 --> 00:12:20,100
[San Kui Tang
Chinese Medicine Prescription]

248
00:12:21,470 --> 00:12:22,450
Uncle.

249
00:12:22,970 --> 00:12:23,570
Uncle.

250
00:12:24,090 --> 00:12:25,090
What happened to you?

251
00:12:26,090 --> 00:12:26,570
Sick?

252
00:12:29,970 --> 00:12:31,250
No.

253
00:12:31,250 --> 00:12:33,050
I found a prescription for you from
an old Chinese medicine doctor.

254
00:12:34,010 --> 00:12:35,410
It is refreshing

255
00:12:35,730 --> 00:12:36,210
and good for your body.

256
00:12:37,010 --> 00:12:39,020
I'm not sick. Why did you do this?

257
00:12:39,810 --> 00:12:41,570
It's for your health.

258
00:12:41,930 --> 00:12:42,890
I've thought about it.

259
00:12:43,770 --> 00:12:45,250
Since you want to go back to school again,

260
00:12:45,620 --> 00:12:47,820
you must want to study well, don't you?

261
00:12:51,250 --> 00:12:52,970
You're growing up so fast.

262
00:12:54,650 --> 00:12:56,330
I don't have any other skills.

263
00:12:57,620 --> 00:12:58,970
I can only afford to send you to school

264
00:12:59,290 --> 00:13:00,480
and hopefully you get into university.

265
00:13:02,530 --> 00:13:03,810
I will then

266
00:13:03,810 --> 00:13:05,650
have no regrets in this life.

267
00:13:07,890 --> 00:13:08,970
Just go for it,

268
00:13:09,330 --> 00:13:10,170
man.

269
00:13:11,610 --> 00:13:12,850
Drink the medicine.

270
00:13:12,850 --> 00:13:13,530
There is still more.

271
00:13:14,350 --> 00:13:16,010
Does it work?

272
00:13:37,180 --> 00:13:39,240
[San Kui Tang
Chinese Medicine Prescription]

273
00:13:49,690 --> 00:13:50,610
Are you okay?

274
00:13:58,050 --> 00:13:59,350
Don't talk to me. I'm studying.

275
00:14:06,890 --> 00:14:08,330
Stop reading. Can you even understand it?

276
00:14:08,330 --> 00:14:09,410
Give it back to me.

277
00:14:09,410 --> 00:14:10,330
Let me read it.

278
00:14:10,330 --> 00:14:11,010
No.

279
00:14:12,330 --> 00:14:12,970
Stop snatching.

280
00:14:14,450 --> 00:14:15,210
Class,

281
00:14:15,410 --> 00:14:16,690
now there's a bad news

282
00:14:16,690 --> 00:14:17,940
and a worse news.

283
00:14:17,940 --> 00:14:18,930
Which one do you want to listen to?

284
00:14:18,930 --> 00:14:19,650
Neither.

285
00:14:19,650 --> 00:14:20,530
You come down.

286
00:14:20,530 --> 00:14:21,730
Listen to me.

287
00:14:22,370 --> 00:14:24,010
The first bad news is that

288
00:14:24,010 --> 00:14:25,100
from today on,

289
00:14:25,100 --> 00:14:26,530
all the minor classes

290
00:14:26,530 --> 00:14:28,250
will be changed to major classes
and self-study.

291
00:14:29,410 --> 00:14:29,940
Game over.

292
00:14:30,170 --> 00:14:31,210
The nightmare has come true.

293
00:14:31,210 --> 00:14:32,970
There's an even worse news.

294
00:14:32,970 --> 00:14:34,810
There will be a parents' mobilization
meeting for the senior-years.

295
00:14:34,810 --> 00:14:36,450
All parents are required to attend.

296
00:14:38,450 --> 00:14:39,250
Parents?

297
00:14:39,850 --> 00:14:40,370
Game over.

298
00:14:41,570 --> 00:14:42,450
I thought I was done for.

299
00:14:44,630 --> 00:14:46,090
[History]

300
00:14:47,730 --> 00:14:48,290
Look at that.

301
00:14:50,130 --> 00:14:50,850
I didn't expect that

302
00:14:51,970 --> 00:14:53,450
you really studied.

303
00:14:54,140 --> 00:14:55,690
Your grades have improved significantly.

304
00:14:56,370 --> 00:14:57,610
I promised you,

305
00:14:57,610 --> 00:14:58,890
I'm just here to try.

306
00:15:00,170 --> 00:15:00,650
Fine.

307
00:15:01,330 --> 00:15:02,370
You kept your word.

308
00:15:03,060 --> 00:15:04,380
But I have to say,

309
00:15:04,380 --> 00:15:06,370
I can't ignore the affairs
between you and Li Qing Tong.

310
00:15:06,580 --> 00:15:07,290
Mr Wu,

311
00:15:07,530 --> 00:15:09,770
I promise I won't make trouble again.

312
00:15:09,770 --> 00:15:12,090
Li Qing Tong is making progress, so am I.

313
00:15:12,090 --> 00:15:13,810
I just need to stay out of trouble.

314
00:15:14,500 --> 00:15:15,690
I don't want to

315
00:15:16,090 --> 00:15:16,810
embarrass her either.

316
00:15:18,410 --> 00:15:19,650
Do you have to sit with her?

317
00:15:21,980 --> 00:15:23,090
All right, that's it.

318
00:15:23,930 --> 00:15:24,890
Listen carefully in class,

319
00:15:24,890 --> 00:15:25,770
and study hard,

320
00:15:25,770 --> 00:15:26,330
understand?

321
00:15:26,820 --> 00:15:27,330
Yes.

322
00:15:27,490 --> 00:15:27,970
Go back to class.

323
00:15:33,980 --> 00:15:34,770
Mr Wu.

324
00:15:35,370 --> 00:15:36,090
Well...

325
00:15:37,330 --> 00:15:37,810
I,

326
00:15:38,330 --> 00:15:39,490
I have another request.

327
00:15:40,140 --> 00:15:40,650
Go ahead.

328
00:15:41,610 --> 00:15:42,130
It's just that...

329
00:15:42,890 --> 00:15:45,530
My uncle is not in good health.

330
00:15:45,530 --> 00:15:46,650
Being back in school again this time

331
00:15:46,650 --> 00:15:47,690
makes him very happy.

332
00:15:47,690 --> 00:15:48,810
He felt hopeful.

333
00:15:48,810 --> 00:15:49,410
So,

334
00:15:50,370 --> 00:15:51,970
can you please not tell him

335
00:15:52,330 --> 00:15:53,450
those things I did?

336
00:15:54,220 --> 00:15:55,490
Then you have to behave well.

337
00:15:55,980 --> 00:15:57,210
I promise I will.

338
00:15:57,210 --> 00:15:58,490
I was

339
00:15:58,490 --> 00:15:59,330
a bit of a jerk before.

340
00:15:59,330 --> 00:16:00,250
That's my character.

341
00:16:00,250 --> 00:16:01,050
I'm sure

342
00:16:01,050 --> 00:16:01,890
I'll fall in line in the future.

343
00:16:01,890 --> 00:16:02,290
I will

344
00:16:03,450 --> 00:16:04,650
get along well with them.

345
00:16:05,530 --> 00:16:06,130
Okay.

346
00:16:07,100 --> 00:16:07,690
Don't worry.

347
00:16:08,090 --> 00:16:09,570
I'm not the kind who likes to
rake up the past.

348
00:16:09,570 --> 00:16:10,770
As long as you behave well,

349
00:16:11,090 --> 00:16:12,090
I won't tell him.

350
00:16:13,170 --> 00:16:13,700
Terrific.

351
00:16:14,050 --> 00:16:14,650
Thanks, sir!

352
00:16:14,650 --> 00:16:15,090
Go back to the class.

353
00:16:16,130 --> 00:16:17,090
Keep fighting.

354
00:16:24,260 --> 00:16:24,770
All right.

355
00:16:26,750 --> 00:16:29,610
[Closed For Today]

356
00:16:31,250 --> 00:16:34,770
I signed my final examination paper
last term.

357
00:16:34,770 --> 00:16:37,650
If my father went to the parents' meeting,
he will know about it.

358
00:16:38,570 --> 00:16:40,090
He's going to beat me.

359
00:16:40,090 --> 00:16:42,810
You signed my examination paper, too.

360
00:16:42,810 --> 00:16:44,530
If my parents know,

361
00:16:44,530 --> 00:16:45,810
I will be history, too.

362
00:16:47,530 --> 00:16:49,250
I am not afraid of this.

363
00:16:49,970 --> 00:16:52,290
My parents know about my grades.

364
00:16:52,290 --> 00:16:55,090
I'm just afraid they know
the other things about me.

365
00:16:56,530 --> 00:16:57,010
Right.

366
00:16:57,530 --> 00:16:59,850
Those things about you can be alarming,

367
00:17:00,330 --> 00:17:03,150
especially the incidents
between you and the boys.

368
00:17:04,099 --> 00:17:05,130
What are you talking about?

369
00:17:05,690 --> 00:17:06,770
Aren't you my friend?

370
00:17:08,060 --> 00:17:09,210
Just admit it.

371
00:17:09,819 --> 00:17:11,890
Your story spread like wildfire

372
00:17:12,530 --> 00:17:13,530
in school.

373
00:17:19,970 --> 00:17:22,050
It's all your fault.
You signed on my examination paper.

374
00:17:22,050 --> 00:17:22,890
Now,

375
00:17:22,890 --> 00:17:24,210
we will be punished when we get home.

376
00:17:24,369 --> 00:17:25,220
What?

377
00:17:25,849 --> 00:17:27,210
All my fault?

378
00:17:27,609 --> 00:17:28,490
You asked me to sign it for you!

379
00:17:28,490 --> 00:17:29,690
Now you say it's my fault?

380
00:17:30,290 --> 00:17:31,290
Fortunately,

381
00:17:31,290 --> 00:17:32,650
I don't have troubles like that.

382
00:17:33,140 --> 00:17:35,690
Do you think it's okay just because
you have good grades?

383
00:17:37,370 --> 00:17:38,540
What troubles did I make?

384
00:17:38,540 --> 00:17:40,010
You got into a fight
in the sports meeting

385
00:17:40,010 --> 00:17:41,570
and cheated for your classmates
in the examination.

386
00:17:41,570 --> 00:17:42,500
Have you forgotten these?

387
00:17:44,330 --> 00:17:45,650
That was old news.

388
00:17:45,650 --> 00:17:46,570
Mr Wu won't talk about them.

389
00:17:46,910 --> 00:17:48,970
Mr Wu won't, but Ms Yang will.

390
00:17:49,410 --> 00:17:50,250
Think about it,

391
00:17:50,250 --> 00:17:52,730
your mother thinks you are a good student.

392
00:17:52,730 --> 00:17:54,330
If Yang Ai Ling tells her those incidents,

393
00:17:54,330 --> 00:17:55,490
think about your mother's temper,

394
00:17:55,490 --> 00:17:56,610
can she not be angry?

395
00:17:57,770 --> 00:17:58,490
That's right.

396
00:18:04,250 --> 00:18:06,490
Only Hua doesn't have these problems.

397
00:18:07,700 --> 00:18:08,580
Please don't say that.

398
00:18:09,020 --> 00:18:09,970
I had a hard time before.

399
00:18:10,490 --> 00:18:12,290
Parents' meeting also caused me
a lot of pain previously.

400
00:18:17,970 --> 00:18:20,020
Why are you so afraid
of the parents' meeting?

401
00:18:20,020 --> 00:18:21,530
This problem can be resolved easily.

402
00:18:21,530 --> 00:18:22,910
You don't need to get all anxious here.

403
00:18:25,150 --> 00:18:26,050
Why are you here?

404
00:18:29,370 --> 00:18:30,530
I experienced

405
00:18:30,530 --> 00:18:31,650
Parentsâ€˜ Mobilization Meeting once.

406
00:18:31,650 --> 00:18:33,410
If you want to slip through,

407
00:18:33,410 --> 00:18:34,250
I have a solution.

408
00:18:35,210 --> 00:18:36,450
Listen to him.

409
00:18:37,010 --> 00:18:37,730
Tell us.

410
00:18:38,730 --> 00:18:40,260
Mobilization meetings are

411
00:18:40,260 --> 00:18:41,490
held by the school directors.

412
00:18:41,490 --> 00:18:43,050
It's a meeting attended
by hundreds of people,

413
00:18:43,050 --> 00:18:44,610
not a small-scale meeting
held in our class.

414
00:18:45,050 --> 00:18:47,370
Hundreds of parents sitting in the hall
at the same time,

415
00:18:47,370 --> 00:18:48,740
so nobody will notice your parents.

416
00:18:48,740 --> 00:18:49,690
So?

417
00:18:49,970 --> 00:18:50,850
So,

418
00:18:51,090 --> 00:18:53,010
find some people to pretend
to be your parents.

419
00:18:53,010 --> 00:18:54,290
These people just need to be

420
00:18:54,290 --> 00:18:55,370
about the age

421
00:18:55,370 --> 00:18:56,010
of your parents.

422
00:18:57,250 --> 00:18:58,050
Sounds possible.

423
00:18:58,650 --> 00:19:00,010
What if the teachers find out?

424
00:19:00,650 --> 00:19:01,250
They won't.

425
00:19:01,250 --> 00:19:02,570
Niu Xiao Huo did it last year.

426
00:19:02,570 --> 00:19:03,570
Nobody noticed it.

427
00:19:04,090 --> 00:19:05,130
Can this work?

428
00:19:05,770 --> 00:19:07,090
I think it is risky.

429
00:19:07,090 --> 00:19:07,970
I think it's a good idea.

430
00:19:08,330 --> 00:19:09,370
Don't do it if you're scared.

431
00:19:13,210 --> 00:19:14,820
But where can we find

432
00:19:15,530 --> 00:19:17,410
so many adults?

433
00:19:19,220 --> 00:19:20,150
I know a way.

434
00:19:20,150 --> 00:19:26,900
[Senior Year Parents' Mobilization Meeting:
10 Years of Hard Work Paying Off in 1 Year]

435
00:19:34,330 --> 00:19:35,890
I'm Pan Yang, my child is...

436
00:19:35,890 --> 00:19:36,380
Got it.

437
00:19:37,050 --> 00:19:37,970
Wang Hong.

438
00:19:37,970 --> 00:19:38,650
Got it.

439
00:19:38,890 --> 00:19:39,650
Zhao Yang.

440
00:19:40,910 --> 00:19:41,890
What's your child's name?

441
00:19:41,890 --> 00:19:42,450
Jia Han Li.

442
00:19:42,450 --> 00:19:44,010
My son's name is Liu Tao.

443
00:19:45,210 --> 00:19:45,770
Liu He.

444
00:19:45,970 --> 00:19:46,490
Got it.

445
00:19:47,730 --> 00:19:48,970
Wang Li Yan.

446
00:19:48,970 --> 00:19:50,290
Dear parents,

447
00:19:50,290 --> 00:19:51,730
good morning.

448
00:19:51,730 --> 00:19:53,810
Thank you for taking time

449
00:19:53,810 --> 00:19:55,090
out of your busy schedule

450
00:19:55,090 --> 00:19:57,490
to participate in this senior year
mobilization meeting.

451
00:20:03,450 --> 00:20:06,450
Now we have entered the major preparation
stage of the college entrance examination.

452
00:20:07,970 --> 00:20:10,160
Are you sure there's no accident?

453
00:20:10,160 --> 00:20:11,210
I'm sure.

454
00:20:11,210 --> 00:20:12,250
There are so many people.

455
00:20:12,250 --> 00:20:13,690
Don't worry.

456
00:20:13,690 --> 00:20:15,410
In the next year,

457
00:20:16,050 --> 00:20:17,810
you should actively cooperate
with the school,

458
00:20:18,970 --> 00:20:20,450
and we will work together

459
00:20:20,450 --> 00:20:22,820
to improve the students' grades.

460
00:20:22,820 --> 00:20:25,130
The following is the main agenda
of the meeting.

461
00:20:26,240 --> 00:20:27,380
[Tieyuan No. 3 Middle School]

462
00:20:45,090 --> 00:20:46,050
Dear parents,

463
00:20:46,050 --> 00:20:47,610
don't leave after the meeting.

464
00:20:48,090 --> 00:20:49,490
Please go to your child's classroom.

465
00:20:50,010 --> 00:20:52,010
The homeroom teacher has
something else to tell you.

466
00:20:56,490 --> 00:20:57,530
How could that be?

467
00:20:57,810 --> 00:20:58,690
Last year,

468
00:20:59,150 --> 00:21:00,210
there was no such arrangement.

469
00:21:01,090 --> 00:21:01,810
Tell me.

470
00:21:02,610 --> 00:21:03,450
Whose idea is this?

471
00:21:10,330 --> 00:21:12,810
You guys always want
to challenge me, right?

472
00:21:13,610 --> 00:21:16,450
You make troubles together
every other day.

473
00:21:17,290 --> 00:21:19,160
If I don't teach you a lesson today,

474
00:21:19,160 --> 00:21:21,460
I can't be the department head.

475
00:21:22,460 --> 00:21:23,340
Go back now

476
00:21:23,850 --> 00:21:25,540
and call your parents here.

477
00:21:25,540 --> 00:21:27,050
I'll have a meeting for them alone.

478
00:21:27,850 --> 00:21:28,570
Ms Yang,

479
00:21:29,130 --> 00:21:29,910
it is just an incident.

480
00:21:30,330 --> 00:21:32,210
Can I talk to my parents by myself?

481
00:21:32,210 --> 00:21:33,490
Shut up and go do it now.

482
00:21:36,770 --> 00:21:37,650
Hurry up!

483
00:21:51,810 --> 00:21:53,450
Your kids

484
00:21:53,850 --> 00:21:55,330
are really amazing.

485
00:21:56,570 --> 00:21:58,220
On such an important

486
00:21:58,730 --> 00:22:00,130
senior year mobilization meeting,

487
00:22:00,860 --> 00:22:02,570
they found some people

488
00:22:02,570 --> 00:22:03,810
who baked sweet potatoes

489
00:22:03,810 --> 00:22:05,090
and sold popcorn

490
00:22:05,090 --> 00:22:05,970
to impersonate you.

491
00:22:07,330 --> 00:22:08,340
Twenty yuan for each.

492
00:22:09,250 --> 00:22:10,570
You guys are really generous.

493
00:22:11,650 --> 00:22:13,770
Why don't you come to me
for such things in the future?

494
00:22:13,770 --> 00:22:14,850
Give me the money,

495
00:22:14,850 --> 00:22:15,570
and I will pretend to be your parent.

496
00:22:20,450 --> 00:22:21,540
These kids,

497
00:22:21,540 --> 00:22:22,490
in our school,

498
00:22:22,490 --> 00:22:23,810
are really famous.

499
00:22:24,570 --> 00:22:25,810
It will take

500
00:22:26,330 --> 00:22:27,730
a long time for me

501
00:22:27,730 --> 00:22:28,700
to finish telling their story.

502
00:22:30,020 --> 00:22:30,650
Ms Yang,

503
00:22:31,340 --> 00:22:33,290
please tell us

504
00:22:33,290 --> 00:22:35,850
what they do in school every day.

505
00:22:35,850 --> 00:22:36,490
Let us know.

506
00:22:36,490 --> 00:22:37,370
Wait,

507
00:22:37,370 --> 00:22:38,130
why aren't you in there?

508
00:22:39,290 --> 00:22:40,530
I didn't do it.

509
00:22:40,530 --> 00:22:41,690
I just helped them with it.

510
00:22:43,050 --> 00:22:44,330
Did you set them up on purpose?

511
00:22:45,330 --> 00:22:45,910
Dude,

512
00:22:46,130 --> 00:22:47,130
of course not.

513
00:22:47,130 --> 00:22:49,050
My uncle and Yang Ai Ling know each other.

514
00:22:49,330 --> 00:22:50,850
I can't do this for myself.

515
00:22:51,810 --> 00:22:53,090
I don't believe you.

516
00:22:53,090 --> 00:22:54,150
It's up to you.

517
00:22:56,610 --> 00:22:57,970
We can start from your son.

518
00:22:59,050 --> 00:23:00,370
During the last sports meeting,

519
00:23:00,910 --> 00:23:03,610
he got into a fight with a senior.

520
00:23:03,610 --> 00:23:04,900
You!

521
00:23:04,900 --> 00:23:06,220
How could you?

522
00:23:07,210 --> 00:23:08,910
You dare to fight those
who are older than you.

523
00:23:12,160 --> 00:23:12,730
Li Wei,

524
00:23:12,730 --> 00:23:14,450
do you know who Chen Jun He's parent is?

525
00:23:14,450 --> 00:23:15,610
Let me ask around.

526
00:23:20,210 --> 00:23:21,330
Don't worry about that.

527
00:23:21,690 --> 00:23:22,730
If he doesn't obey you,

528
00:23:22,730 --> 00:23:23,650
I'll beat the hell out of him.

529
00:23:23,650 --> 00:23:24,850
The child needs guiding.

530
00:23:24,850 --> 00:23:26,050
Why is he here?

531
00:23:32,810 --> 00:23:33,530
Jin Bu, Jin Bu.

532
00:23:33,770 --> 00:23:35,090
That's him.

533
00:23:38,850 --> 00:23:40,370
Puppy love must be controlled.

534
00:23:40,370 --> 00:23:40,850
Yes.

535
00:23:48,810 --> 00:23:49,490
What are you doing?

536
00:23:49,490 --> 00:23:50,370
What do you want to do?

537
00:23:50,370 --> 00:23:51,890
I warn you not to go to my uncle.

538
00:23:51,890 --> 00:23:52,690
If you dare talk nonsense with him,

539
00:23:52,690 --> 00:23:53,860
believe it or not, I will deal with you.

540
00:23:54,810 --> 00:23:55,930
You are afraid of someone, too.

541
00:23:57,290 --> 00:23:58,890
Stay away from Li Qing Tong,

542
00:23:59,210 --> 00:24:00,460
or I'll still go to your uncle.

543
00:24:04,290 --> 00:24:05,650
What do you want?

544
00:24:06,850 --> 00:24:08,090
Don't start it.

545
00:24:08,770 --> 00:24:09,910
Go to the parents?

546
00:24:09,910 --> 00:24:10,890
I can, too.

547
00:24:11,450 --> 00:24:12,410
Who can you go to?

548
00:24:13,010 --> 00:24:14,490
You think I know nothing about you.

549
00:24:15,100 --> 00:24:16,690
Ye Zi made the call for you, right?

550
00:24:19,150 --> 00:24:20,410
If you're not afraid of
me telling the others,

551
00:24:20,410 --> 00:24:21,330
just try.

552
00:24:21,610 --> 00:24:23,150
We will go down together.

553
00:24:31,380 --> 00:24:32,770
Excuse me.
Are you Mr. Wu Di Bao?

554
00:24:33,260 --> 00:24:34,410
I am. Who are you?

555
00:24:34,410 --> 00:24:35,460
I'm Wu Zhi Xun's father.

556
00:24:36,130 --> 00:24:37,290
Please come in.

557
00:24:37,970 --> 00:24:38,890
Have a seat.

558
00:24:41,770 --> 00:24:42,890
You are here for...

559
00:24:43,330 --> 00:24:45,050
I'm here to talk to you

560
00:24:45,490 --> 00:24:46,690
about Wu Zhi Xun's recent situation.

561
00:24:47,530 --> 00:24:49,490
He has done well recently.

562
00:24:50,150 --> 00:24:52,690
Didn't you notice that his performance
has dropped recently?

563
00:24:53,910 --> 00:24:56,890
I think it's within a reasonable range.

564
00:24:57,330 --> 00:24:58,250
I don't think so.

565
00:24:59,290 --> 00:25:00,610
I heard that

566
00:25:00,610 --> 00:25:03,050
he is tutoring a girl all day.

567
00:25:03,450 --> 00:25:04,130
Is that true?

568
00:25:05,010 --> 00:25:06,210
That's a plan

569
00:25:06,210 --> 00:25:08,290
of our study group.

570
00:25:08,970 --> 00:25:11,490
It is a process in which
students improve with each other.

571
00:25:11,490 --> 00:25:12,850
I don't think it will improve each other.

572
00:25:13,370 --> 00:25:14,050
Mr Wu,

573
00:25:14,740 --> 00:25:16,150
I hope you can get him

574
00:25:16,150 --> 00:25:17,210
out of this activity.

575
00:25:21,290 --> 00:25:22,010
Sir,

576
00:25:22,010 --> 00:25:22,610
well,

577
00:25:22,610 --> 00:25:23,810
now the situation is,

578
00:25:24,450 --> 00:25:27,250
Wu Zhi Xun has few friends in school.

579
00:25:28,050 --> 00:25:29,730
So I think it's not a bad thing

580
00:25:29,730 --> 00:25:32,150
to share his experience
with his classmates,

581
00:25:32,150 --> 00:25:32,610
right?

582
00:25:32,610 --> 00:25:34,890
And I don't think there is any problem

583
00:25:34,890 --> 00:25:36,210
with his performance at present.

584
00:25:37,250 --> 00:25:39,770
After all, we can't be
too hard on children,

585
00:25:39,770 --> 00:25:40,490
right?

586
00:25:40,910 --> 00:25:41,530
Mr Wu,

587
00:25:42,910 --> 00:25:44,090
if you have this attitude,

588
00:25:44,410 --> 00:25:45,490
I'll have to have words with you.

589
00:25:45,850 --> 00:25:47,650
Wu Zhi Xun comes to this school

590
00:25:48,010 --> 00:25:49,290
not for friendship,

591
00:25:49,650 --> 00:25:51,490
but for lofty ideals and aspirations.

592
00:25:51,490 --> 00:25:54,020
If there is any barrier
in his study in the future,

593
00:25:54,020 --> 00:25:55,610
I will talk to your principal directly.

594
00:25:57,650 --> 00:25:59,010
Don't be angry, sir.
You...

595
00:26:02,380 --> 00:26:03,410
He's too hot-tempered.

596
00:26:05,610 --> 00:26:06,490
You wicked girl!

597
00:26:06,490 --> 00:26:07,340
Dad!

598
00:26:07,340 --> 00:26:08,100
I pay for you to go to school,

599
00:26:08,100 --> 00:26:09,450
but you found so many troubles.

600
00:26:09,450 --> 00:26:10,690
How did the fight start?

601
00:26:10,690 --> 00:26:12,130
Are you trying to piss me off?

602
00:26:12,130 --> 00:26:13,730
No, let me explain!

603
00:26:13,730 --> 00:26:14,210
Mom!

604
00:26:14,210 --> 00:26:15,050
No need to explain!

605
00:26:15,610 --> 00:26:16,910
I'll beat you to death today!

606
00:26:19,010 --> 00:26:19,810
You know what?

607
00:26:20,290 --> 00:26:21,450
She instigated the boys

608
00:26:21,450 --> 00:26:22,650
to rewrite grades!

609
00:26:22,650 --> 00:26:23,050
I...

610
00:26:23,050 --> 00:26:24,060
How can you do it!

611
00:26:24,060 --> 00:26:25,380
It's all rumors.

612
00:26:25,380 --> 00:26:26,970
Mom, how can you believe it?

613
00:26:26,970 --> 00:26:27,810
Well, honey,

614
00:26:27,810 --> 00:26:28,770
don't do this, please.

615
00:26:28,770 --> 00:26:30,330
She is our own daughter.

616
00:26:30,330 --> 00:26:31,250
Our daughter?

617
00:26:31,570 --> 00:26:32,570
You look at her!

618
00:26:33,010 --> 00:26:34,620
Is she really my daughter?

619
00:26:34,620 --> 00:26:35,370
Yes, Yes.

620
00:26:35,370 --> 00:26:37,330
I saw you giving birth to her that year.

621
00:26:37,330 --> 00:26:38,050
Go away!

622
00:26:38,050 --> 00:26:38,490
Wait.

623
00:26:38,920 --> 00:26:40,610
Don't be angry, aunt.

624
00:26:41,660 --> 00:26:42,090
Hua,

625
00:26:42,770 --> 00:26:43,810
I'm just starting to talk about you.

626
00:26:44,420 --> 00:26:45,770
I thought

627
00:26:45,770 --> 00:26:47,910
you could get Li Qing Tong to study hard.

628
00:26:47,910 --> 00:26:48,650
I didn't expect that

629
00:26:49,150 --> 00:26:50,970
they were in the same boat.

630
00:26:51,410 --> 00:26:52,210
You,

631
00:26:52,210 --> 00:26:54,410
are you worthy of my care, Hua?

632
00:26:54,910 --> 00:26:56,570
Sorry, aunt. It's my fault!

633
00:26:56,740 --> 00:26:57,450
There won't be

634
00:26:57,650 --> 00:26:59,210
a next time.

635
00:26:59,210 --> 00:27:00,050
Yes.

636
00:27:00,260 --> 00:27:01,610
The child is wrong,

637
00:27:01,610 --> 00:27:03,250
but it's not a huge mistake.

638
00:27:03,250 --> 00:27:03,910
What?

639
00:27:04,530 --> 00:27:05,730
If you're still angry,

640
00:27:05,730 --> 00:27:07,250
hit me instead.

641
00:27:07,650 --> 00:27:08,150
I...

642
00:27:11,210 --> 00:27:12,810
Li Wu Si.

643
00:27:14,130 --> 00:27:17,150
You're working together
to bully me, aren't you?

644
00:27:17,150 --> 00:27:17,540
No!

645
00:27:18,370 --> 00:27:20,250
I can't take this any longer.

646
00:27:20,250 --> 00:27:20,810
Feng Xia.

647
00:27:23,450 --> 00:27:24,050
Feng Xia.

648
00:27:24,370 --> 00:27:24,890
Feng Xia.

649
00:27:25,970 --> 00:27:26,970
Open the door, Feng Xia!

650
00:27:26,970 --> 00:27:27,250
I...

651
00:27:28,910 --> 00:27:29,610
Feng Xia.

652
00:27:29,860 --> 00:27:30,300
[Mu Dan Hotel]

653
00:27:30,300 --> 00:27:30,910
Mom,

654
00:27:30,910 --> 00:27:31,620
just calm down

655
00:27:31,620 --> 00:27:32,450
and listen to me.

656
00:27:32,450 --> 00:27:34,210
At least I didn't affect my studies.

657
00:27:34,450 --> 00:27:34,890
Dad,

658
00:27:34,890 --> 00:27:35,770
I'm really not the mastermind.

659
00:27:36,090 --> 00:27:37,040
They instigated me to do it.

660
00:27:37,040 --> 00:27:38,130
[Daily Necessity Supermarket
and Restaurant]

661
00:27:38,130 --> 00:27:40,090
You two are always fighting.

662
00:27:40,090 --> 00:27:41,490
I have a trauma now.

663
00:27:41,490 --> 00:27:43,500
Why don't you just get a divorce?

664
00:27:45,200 --> 00:27:47,440
[Tieyuan No. 3 Middle School]

665
00:27:47,540 --> 00:27:50,810
[Chen Jun He is a scumbag!]

666
00:27:50,810 --> 00:27:51,330
That scumbag!

667
00:27:53,740 --> 00:27:54,620
This is insane.

668
00:27:55,850 --> 00:27:57,150
They won't give me any pocket money.

669
00:27:57,810 --> 00:27:59,150
How can I live now?

670
00:28:01,290 --> 00:28:02,650
Pocket money?

671
00:28:03,050 --> 00:28:05,130
My parents won't even let me eat.

672
00:28:05,130 --> 00:28:07,160
They want me to starve for a few meals
and reflect on it.

673
00:28:07,570 --> 00:28:09,330
I'm so hungry that I'm thin now.

674
00:28:10,530 --> 00:28:11,450
Don't worry.

675
00:28:12,090 --> 00:28:12,890
You are not thin.

676
00:28:13,730 --> 00:28:14,370
Go away!

677
00:28:15,090 --> 00:28:17,150
We shouldn't have done that.

678
00:28:17,410 --> 00:28:18,810
I have warned you.

679
00:28:19,160 --> 00:28:20,490
It's too late now.

680
00:28:22,850 --> 00:28:25,130
Chen Jun He is really something.

681
00:28:25,130 --> 00:28:26,570
He helped us find someone
to pretend to be our parents,

682
00:28:26,570 --> 00:28:27,770
but he didn't find one for himself.

683
00:28:27,770 --> 00:28:28,970
Did he do it on purpose?

684
00:28:29,290 --> 00:28:30,160
I don't think so.

685
00:28:31,810 --> 00:28:33,650
His uncle and Yang Ai Ling
know each other well.

686
00:28:33,900 --> 00:28:34,970
He won't dare to do that.

687
00:28:36,290 --> 00:28:38,010
And he's been well-behaved these days.

688
00:28:38,010 --> 00:28:39,210
It's all temporary.

689
00:28:39,810 --> 00:28:41,850
Who doesn't hold back
before the parents' meeting?

690
00:28:41,850 --> 00:28:43,610
We should not have trusted him.

691
00:28:45,250 --> 00:28:47,170
Can we leave him alone in the future?

692
00:28:47,690 --> 00:28:49,970
Otherwise you will not see me alive.

693
00:28:57,260 --> 00:28:59,520
[Chen Jun He is a scumbag!]

694
00:29:03,060 --> 00:29:04,820
I'm so proud of you guys.

695
00:29:06,810 --> 00:29:08,170
Our class is really outstanding

696
00:29:09,450 --> 00:29:11,250
at this mobilization meeting.

697
00:29:12,130 --> 00:29:13,850
Am I too lenient to you?

698
00:29:15,770 --> 00:29:17,090
You are all lawless.

699
00:29:17,450 --> 00:29:19,490
Have you ever paid attention
to the school spirit and discipline?

700
00:29:21,100 --> 00:29:22,330
What do you want to do?

701
00:29:22,330 --> 00:29:23,530
Don't you want to go on to school?

702
00:29:24,740 --> 00:29:25,850
What should you do now?

703
00:29:25,850 --> 00:29:26,970
Look back.

704
00:29:26,970 --> 00:29:27,770
You are already in your senior year.

705
00:29:27,770 --> 00:29:29,140
There are only 260 days left.

706
00:29:29,610 --> 00:29:30,370
But what are you doing?

707
00:29:31,010 --> 00:29:31,810
What are the other classes doing?

708
00:29:32,220 --> 00:29:33,410
Go all out to revise

709
00:29:33,410 --> 00:29:34,730
to get better grades.

710
00:29:34,730 --> 00:29:35,370
What about you?

711
00:29:36,690 --> 00:29:37,690
Are you worthy?

712
00:29:38,410 --> 00:29:39,650
Worthy of me?

713
00:29:39,650 --> 00:29:40,810
Worthy of your parents?

714
00:29:40,810 --> 00:29:42,490
Worthy of your study all these years?

715
00:29:42,490 --> 00:29:43,890
Wang Xiao Min, why did you nod?

716
00:29:43,890 --> 00:29:44,850
Go out!

717
00:29:45,490 --> 00:29:46,090
All three of you too, go out!

718
00:29:46,090 --> 00:29:46,610
Hurry!

719
00:29:48,250 --> 00:29:49,130
Hurry up!

720
00:29:52,610 --> 00:29:54,340
What are you still looking at?

721
00:29:56,930 --> 00:29:57,860
Go out from the back door!

722
00:30:01,010 --> 00:30:02,730
Write a 10,000 words reflective report!

723
00:30:12,250 --> 00:30:13,210
I'm warning all of you.

724
00:30:14,250 --> 00:30:16,250
I hope this is the last time
I receive your reflective report.

725
00:30:16,730 --> 00:30:17,850
Take responsibility of your own life.

726
00:30:24,930 --> 00:30:26,670
[Tieyuan No. 3 Middle School]

727
00:30:38,940 --> 00:30:40,120
[Come to the rooftop after school]

728
00:31:06,770 --> 00:31:07,690
Why do you want to see me?

729
00:31:09,010 --> 00:31:10,260
How much do you know?

730
00:31:10,650 --> 00:31:11,690
Know what?

731
00:31:12,090 --> 00:31:12,930
About the call.

732
00:31:13,930 --> 00:31:14,970
I know all about it.

733
00:31:15,730 --> 00:31:17,570
She pretended to be your mother

734
00:31:17,570 --> 00:31:19,060
and pretended to have known you are here.

735
00:31:19,500 --> 00:31:21,130
And she told Li Qing Tong's parents that

736
00:31:21,130 --> 00:31:23,170
she would like you to study here.

737
00:31:23,170 --> 00:31:23,810
Right?

738
00:31:24,290 --> 00:31:26,010
Why didn't Ye Zi keep her promise?

739
00:31:26,570 --> 00:31:27,450
She didn't tell me.

740
00:31:27,450 --> 00:31:28,330
I overheard it.

741
00:31:28,330 --> 00:31:29,210
Don't blame her.

742
00:31:31,130 --> 00:31:32,330
You can't tell the others.

743
00:31:33,810 --> 00:31:35,460
That's up to your performance.

744
00:31:38,100 --> 00:31:38,730
What do you want?

745
00:31:39,290 --> 00:31:40,890
If you promise me not to
harass Li Qing Tong anymore,

746
00:31:41,130 --> 00:31:42,970
we won't bother each other.

747
00:31:42,970 --> 00:31:43,890
Are you kidding?

748
00:31:43,890 --> 00:31:45,370
Why should I promise you?

749
00:31:45,370 --> 00:31:46,370
You don't have to worry about us.

750
00:31:46,850 --> 00:31:47,850
You two...

751
00:31:48,810 --> 00:31:50,650
You two cost me seventeen years of youth.

752
00:31:51,010 --> 00:31:52,290
Why shouldn't I worry?

753
00:31:52,290 --> 00:31:55,290
Don't think that you can be together

754
00:31:55,290 --> 00:31:57,410
after pestering Li Qing Tong every day.

755
00:31:58,090 --> 00:32:00,130
You look like you're all right now,

756
00:32:00,130 --> 00:32:01,540
and do whatever you want to do.

757
00:32:01,540 --> 00:32:03,370
You will only be more and more
irresponsible in the future.

758
00:32:03,370 --> 00:32:04,970
Li Qing Tong is not a child's toy.

759
00:32:04,970 --> 00:32:06,210
You can't take her
just because you like her,

760
00:32:06,210 --> 00:32:07,610
and get rid of her when you don't.

761
00:32:07,610 --> 00:32:08,890
Scums like you

762
00:32:08,890 --> 00:32:10,130
don't deserve her at all!

763
00:32:10,130 --> 00:32:12,050
I won't let you pester her anymore.

764
00:32:12,490 --> 00:32:13,290
If you do that again,

765
00:32:13,930 --> 00:32:15,850
I'll tell your uncle everything about you.

766
00:32:16,290 --> 00:32:17,690
If your uncle can't control you,

767
00:32:18,050 --> 00:32:19,770
I'll tell Yang Ai Ling, or the principal.

768
00:32:20,020 --> 00:32:21,450
I don't believe nobody can control you.

769
00:32:23,540 --> 00:32:24,210
How dare you!

770
00:32:24,690 --> 00:32:25,930
Then I will tell Li Qing Tong's parents

771
00:32:25,930 --> 00:32:27,330
all about you.

772
00:32:27,770 --> 00:32:28,820
Neither of us can have it good.

773
00:32:29,970 --> 00:32:30,650
It's up to you.

774
00:32:32,020 --> 00:32:33,010
If I don't get to study,

775
00:32:33,890 --> 00:32:34,770
you can't, too.

776
00:32:36,570 --> 00:32:37,370
Let me go!

777
00:32:38,970 --> 00:32:39,650
Chen Jun He.

778
00:32:44,370 --> 00:32:44,850
Li Qing Tong.

779
00:32:44,850 --> 00:32:46,490
How dare you hit her!

780
00:32:48,570 --> 00:32:49,130
Li Qing Tong.

781
00:32:49,650 --> 00:32:50,290
Li Qing Tong.

782
00:33:09,650 --> 00:33:10,450
Mr Wu,

783
00:33:10,450 --> 00:33:11,410
something happened.

784
00:33:11,410 --> 00:33:12,050
What?

785
00:33:15,810 --> 00:33:16,930
Stop playing.

786
00:33:17,730 --> 00:33:19,250
Li Qing Tong is in the hospital.
Come quickly.

787
00:33:19,250 --> 00:33:19,970
What?

788
00:33:19,970 --> 00:33:20,690
Hurry up!

789
00:33:23,770 --> 00:33:24,650
Nurse,

790
00:33:25,410 --> 00:33:26,490
is Li Qing Tong okay?

791
00:33:26,850 --> 00:33:27,610
She's having a checkup.

792
00:33:27,610 --> 00:33:28,460
Just wait for the result.

793
00:33:30,530 --> 00:33:31,570
I think she's okay.

794
00:33:31,570 --> 00:33:32,970
Call her parents first.

795
00:33:32,970 --> 00:33:33,810
Okay.

796
00:33:37,650 --> 00:33:38,930
Are you happy now?

797
00:33:52,730 --> 00:33:53,450
Hello?

798
00:34:07,690 --> 00:34:08,330
Hey...

799
00:34:09,889 --> 00:34:10,810
Hua.

800
00:34:12,090 --> 00:34:14,650
If anything happens to me,

801
00:34:15,340 --> 00:34:18,610
you must remember to

802
00:34:19,130 --> 00:34:21,889
take good care of my parents.

803
00:34:21,889 --> 00:34:23,330
Come on,

804
00:34:23,330 --> 00:34:24,210
stop acting.

805
00:34:24,580 --> 00:34:26,250
The doctor said you didn't get hurt.

806
00:34:26,570 --> 00:34:27,610
It was just appendicitis.

807
00:34:29,650 --> 00:34:30,810
You are so boring.

808
00:34:31,810 --> 00:34:34,929
I finally became the female lead
on a hospital bed,

809
00:34:35,139 --> 00:34:37,370
but you don't even want to play along.

810
00:34:38,810 --> 00:34:39,659
Where?

811
00:34:39,659 --> 00:34:40,420
Where?

812
00:34:40,420 --> 00:34:41,330
Where did you get hurt?

813
00:34:41,330 --> 00:34:42,850
Mr Wu, she's fine.

814
00:34:42,850 --> 00:34:44,449
She had a sudden appendicitis attack.

815
00:34:44,940 --> 00:34:45,730
Appendicitis?

816
00:34:45,730 --> 00:34:47,010
Didn't she get beaten?

817
00:34:47,010 --> 00:34:48,020
Who beat our daughter?

818
00:34:48,460 --> 00:34:49,449
Who beat our daughter?

819
00:34:49,449 --> 00:34:50,330
No one did, aunt.

820
00:34:50,510 --> 00:34:51,980
She had a sudden appendicitis attack.

821
00:34:53,090 --> 00:34:53,929
Appendicitis.

822
00:34:54,250 --> 00:34:56,290
Who mentioned getting beaten? You?

823
00:34:56,290 --> 00:34:57,890
Madam, it was a slip of tongue.

824
00:34:58,770 --> 00:34:59,570
Mr Wu,

825
00:34:59,730 --> 00:35:02,010
she was fine before she went to school.

826
00:35:02,290 --> 00:35:03,450
Why is she sick now?

827
00:35:03,890 --> 00:35:05,730
Why is she in hospital now?

828
00:35:05,730 --> 00:35:07,130
I'm to blame for this.

829
00:35:07,890 --> 00:35:08,610
Mom,

830
00:35:08,610 --> 00:35:10,610
what does this have to do with Mr Wu?

831
00:35:10,610 --> 00:35:11,900
Did you get it from school?

832
00:35:11,900 --> 00:35:13,250
You really don't know
anything about medicine.

833
00:35:13,250 --> 00:35:15,210
I can't just get appendicitis from school.

834
00:35:15,210 --> 00:35:16,030
I know nothing about medicine.

835
00:35:16,520 --> 00:35:17,370
But I know you.

836
00:35:20,730 --> 00:35:21,290
What happened?

837
00:35:21,890 --> 00:35:22,370
What?

838
00:35:22,370 --> 00:35:23,030
It hurts.

839
00:35:23,030 --> 00:35:23,850
It hurts.

840
00:35:23,850 --> 00:35:25,210
It really hurts.

841
00:35:25,210 --> 00:35:25,730
Is it starting to hurt again?

842
00:35:26,690 --> 00:35:27,300
Nurse.

843
00:35:27,490 --> 00:35:28,180
Nurse.

844
00:35:28,180 --> 00:35:31,170
Is that how you treat patients?

845
00:35:31,170 --> 00:35:32,330
Are you acting? Does it really hurt?

846
00:35:32,330 --> 00:35:33,850
It's real!

847
00:35:35,660 --> 00:35:36,890
Wait for me.

848
00:35:36,890 --> 00:35:37,650
I will.

849
00:35:37,650 --> 00:35:38,650
Please wait outside.

850
00:35:41,690 --> 00:35:43,290
Mom's here waiting for you.

851
00:35:44,900 --> 00:35:45,490
Tong Tong.

852
00:35:52,370 --> 00:35:53,650
Would you like to have a seat first?

853
00:35:55,730 --> 00:35:56,370
Aunt.

854
00:36:01,250 --> 00:36:02,410
My daughter.

855
00:36:03,030 --> 00:36:04,290
Tong Tong.

856
00:36:15,010 --> 00:36:16,330
Tong Tong.

857
00:36:19,970 --> 00:36:20,570
Liu Feng Xia.

858
00:36:21,030 --> 00:36:21,660
Liu Feng Xia.

859
00:36:22,690 --> 00:36:23,510
What happened?

860
00:36:23,510 --> 00:36:24,740
Why you are crying? Liu Feng Xia?

861
00:36:25,510 --> 00:36:26,500
What happened to my daughter?

862
00:36:27,330 --> 00:36:27,820
Tong Tong...

863
00:36:27,820 --> 00:36:28,970
What happened to my daughter? Tell me!

864
00:36:28,970 --> 00:36:29,690
Tong Tong...

865
00:36:30,490 --> 00:36:31,970
Sir, she's fine.

866
00:36:31,970 --> 00:36:32,890
It's just appendicitis.

867
00:36:32,890 --> 00:36:33,730
Just a minor illness.

868
00:36:34,030 --> 00:36:35,690
Minor illness?

869
00:36:35,690 --> 00:36:37,010
She's not your daughter,

870
00:36:37,010 --> 00:36:38,610
so you don't care.

871
00:36:39,730 --> 00:36:40,610
Li.

872
00:36:40,610 --> 00:36:43,410
Tong Tong is already not very clever.

873
00:36:43,410 --> 00:36:45,090
Now she is taking so much anesthetics.

874
00:36:45,570 --> 00:36:47,290
Could it affect her
college entrance examination?

875
00:36:47,290 --> 00:36:50,260
What should we do?

876
00:36:50,700 --> 00:36:53,210
Liu Feng Xia, I think you are the one
who is not clever here.

877
00:36:53,810 --> 00:36:56,410
It's just appendicitis.
Why are you crying so much?

878
00:36:56,410 --> 00:36:58,300
You scared the hell out of me.

879
00:36:58,300 --> 00:37:00,290
I rushed here from the construction site.

880
00:37:00,810 --> 00:37:02,130
This is not that serious.

881
00:37:02,130 --> 00:37:03,330
Why isn't this not serious?

882
00:37:03,690 --> 00:37:04,970
Isn't she your daughter?

883
00:37:04,970 --> 00:37:06,410
But appendicitis is just a minor illness.

884
00:37:06,410 --> 00:37:08,090
You sounded like it was something serious.

885
00:37:08,650 --> 00:37:11,510
She is in the operating room now.
How can it be a minor illness?

886
00:37:20,910 --> 00:37:21,770
Mr Wu.

887
00:37:22,290 --> 00:37:22,770
Sir...

888
00:37:23,010 --> 00:37:23,450
You...

889
00:37:23,450 --> 00:37:24,290
Why are you here?

890
00:37:24,610 --> 00:37:25,410
The child is ill.

891
00:37:25,410 --> 00:37:26,330
I am here to see her.

892
00:37:27,020 --> 00:37:27,490
You shouldn't have to.

893
00:37:27,490 --> 00:37:28,490
You are a busy man,

894
00:37:28,490 --> 00:37:28,970
right?

895
00:37:28,970 --> 00:37:29,970
We can't trouble you.

896
00:37:29,970 --> 00:37:30,490
Everything is fine.

897
00:37:30,490 --> 00:37:31,570
It's just a minor illness.

898
00:37:31,570 --> 00:37:33,370
Her mother and I will wait for her here.

899
00:37:33,620 --> 00:37:34,730
Please go back to your work.

900
00:37:34,730 --> 00:37:36,170
I can stay here to wait for her.

901
00:37:36,170 --> 00:37:36,890
It's fine.

902
00:37:36,890 --> 00:37:38,210
You are a busy man.

903
00:37:38,210 --> 00:37:38,690
Well then.

904
00:37:38,690 --> 00:37:40,410
Call me if you need anything, Madam.

905
00:37:41,290 --> 00:37:42,170
I'll see you off, Mr Wu.

906
00:37:42,170 --> 00:37:43,210
Hua, see Mr Wu off.

907
00:37:43,210 --> 00:37:43,810
It's fine.

908
00:37:43,810 --> 00:37:44,650
Drive safe.

909
00:37:44,650 --> 00:37:45,170
Okay.

910
00:37:45,170 --> 00:37:45,940
Don't worry.

911
00:37:51,660 --> 00:37:52,330
Go back in.

912
00:37:53,250 --> 00:37:54,370
Have a safe trip back, Mr Wu.

913
00:37:54,370 --> 00:37:54,810
Okay.

914
00:37:57,290 --> 00:37:58,010
Swift Leg.

915
00:38:01,020 --> 00:38:02,690
Take this money and pay
the medical expenses for Li Qing Tong.

916
00:38:03,090 --> 00:38:03,970
Tell me if it's not enough.

917
00:38:04,170 --> 00:38:04,930
I'll think of something.

918
00:38:05,610 --> 00:38:06,210
You don't need to.

919
00:38:06,930 --> 00:38:07,490
Take it.

920
00:38:08,410 --> 00:38:09,570
I should pay for it.

921
00:38:13,250 --> 00:38:14,770
How did you get so much money?

922
00:38:15,210 --> 00:38:16,420
It's my own money. Stop asking.

923
00:38:16,770 --> 00:38:17,300
Wait...

924
00:38:17,300 --> 00:38:17,810
By the way,

925
00:38:18,650 --> 00:38:20,010
don't tell Li Qing Tong about the money.

926
00:38:38,290 --> 00:38:39,170
Don't worry.

927
00:38:39,730 --> 00:38:40,690
I'll think of something

928
00:38:42,510 --> 00:38:43,820
to raise the money this time.

929
00:38:45,140 --> 00:38:46,290
What can you do?

930
00:38:48,930 --> 00:38:50,420
You can't borrow money any more.

931
00:38:54,850 --> 00:38:55,570
I know.

932
00:38:58,340 --> 00:38:59,340
I think

933
00:38:59,340 --> 00:38:59,970
we can...

934
00:39:00,490 --> 00:39:01,450
Stop.

935
00:39:04,620 --> 00:39:05,130
Hua,

936
00:39:05,730 --> 00:39:06,490
well,

937
00:39:08,610 --> 00:39:10,810
you stay with your aunt.

938
00:39:10,810 --> 00:39:11,930
I'm going to pay for the money.

939
00:39:11,930 --> 00:39:13,130
I have already paid for it, uncle.

940
00:39:14,410 --> 00:39:14,930
What?

941
00:39:17,610 --> 00:39:19,140
Where did you get the money from?

942
00:39:21,290 --> 00:39:22,370
From my mom.

943
00:39:23,370 --> 00:39:24,690
Kid,

944
00:39:25,330 --> 00:39:27,610
how can we use the money
your mother gave you?

945
00:39:27,610 --> 00:39:28,770
Let's go and get back the money.

946
00:39:28,770 --> 00:39:29,380
Uncle.

947
00:39:30,370 --> 00:39:32,330
I've been living in your house
for such a long time.

948
00:39:32,330 --> 00:39:33,510
I ate and spend your money.

949
00:39:33,510 --> 00:39:35,370
I feel sorry about it.

950
00:39:35,370 --> 00:39:37,030
Please treat the money as
my food and daily expenses.

951
00:39:37,490 --> 00:39:37,970
Hua,

952
00:39:37,970 --> 00:39:40,410
we won't be happy if you say this.

953
00:39:40,850 --> 00:39:42,510
Although our family is not rich,

954
00:39:42,770 --> 00:39:44,690
we can afford to feed you.

955
00:39:45,370 --> 00:39:46,370
Even if you live here forever,

956
00:39:46,370 --> 00:39:47,490
the both of us

957
00:39:47,490 --> 00:39:48,740
will not shun you.

958
00:39:50,030 --> 00:39:51,330
If you see it that way,

959
00:39:51,330 --> 00:39:52,510
we have to return the money to you.

960
00:39:52,510 --> 00:39:52,850
Come.

961
00:39:52,850 --> 00:39:54,770
Let's just treat it as money
Li Qing Tong borrowed from me.

962
00:39:55,030 --> 00:39:56,170
She is eighteen years old.

963
00:39:56,170 --> 00:39:57,730
She should pay for
her own medical expenses.

964
00:39:58,090 --> 00:39:59,650
I'll have her write me a loan note
when she's out of hospital.

965
00:39:59,650 --> 00:40:00,930
I'm sure she'll pay me back.

966
00:40:01,510 --> 00:40:02,610
Can we do that?

967
00:40:12,330 --> 00:40:13,250
Li.

968
00:40:14,490 --> 00:40:15,130
Look.

969
00:40:16,010 --> 00:40:17,930
This is the kid's good intention.

970
00:40:18,850 --> 00:40:20,330
Besides, Li Qing Tong is my...

971
00:40:21,860 --> 00:40:23,030
My good friend.

972
00:40:23,510 --> 00:40:24,770
I want to do something for her.

973
00:40:32,510 --> 00:40:33,090
Hua,

974
00:40:33,610 --> 00:40:35,410
I'll write you the loan note.

975
00:40:35,410 --> 00:40:37,030
I will pay you back. I promise.

976
00:40:38,210 --> 00:40:38,930
Thank you.

977
00:40:40,510 --> 00:40:41,010
Jin Bu.

978
00:40:41,490 --> 00:40:42,250
Jin Bu.

979
00:40:42,570 --> 00:40:42,930
Shui Shui.

980
00:40:42,930 --> 00:40:43,730
Uncle. Auntie.

981
00:40:43,730 --> 00:40:44,650
How is Li Qing Tong?

982
00:40:46,010 --> 00:40:46,970
She is undergoing an operation.

983
00:40:47,210 --> 00:40:47,650
Is she okay?

984
00:40:47,650 --> 00:40:48,380
Yes.

985
00:40:48,780 --> 00:40:54,630
[Operating Room]

986
00:40:55,570 --> 00:40:56,890
What on earth happened?

987
00:40:57,930 --> 00:40:58,810
Keep your voice down.

988
00:40:59,290 --> 00:40:59,970
We are in the hospital.

989
00:41:00,410 --> 00:41:01,650
I heard it's because of Chen Jun He.

990
00:41:02,020 --> 00:41:02,650
What?

991
00:41:03,290 --> 00:41:04,810
Chen Jun He hit Li Qing Tong?

992
00:41:05,570 --> 00:41:06,690
Isn't he too ruthless?

993
00:41:06,980 --> 00:41:07,570
No, wait.

994
00:41:08,250 --> 00:41:10,410
I have a little conflict with Chen Jun He.

995
00:41:10,410 --> 00:41:11,690
Then Li Qing Tong came to drag him away

996
00:41:11,690 --> 00:41:13,170
but she fell down accidentally.

997
00:41:13,170 --> 00:41:14,510
And the appendicitis happened.

998
00:41:14,510 --> 00:41:15,690
He came at you.

999
00:41:16,330 --> 00:41:17,210
Are you okay?

1000
00:41:17,210 --> 00:41:18,010
I'm fine.

1001
00:41:18,330 --> 00:41:19,130
I didn't fight with him.

1002
00:41:23,410 --> 00:41:24,090
Duan Xiao.

1003
00:41:28,510 --> 00:41:29,570
What does he want to do?

1004
00:41:29,970 --> 00:41:30,740
I don't know.

1005
00:41:51,410 --> 00:41:52,330
Chen Jun He!
